Indonesia Stocks: AKR Corporindo, Bumi Resources, Indofood CBP

-- B y   B e r n i   M o e s t a f a
-- 
2011-02-23T09:38:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/indonesia-stocks-akr-corporindo-energi-mega-medco-energi.html
Shares of the following companies
had unusual moves in Indonesian trading. Stock symbols are in
parentheses, and prices are as of the 4 p.m. Jakarta time close.  The  Jakarta Composite index  advanced 23.02 points, or 0.7
percent, to 3,474.12, gaining for the first time in three days.  Coal producers: PT Bumi Resources (BUMI IJ),  Asia ’s largest
exporter of power-station coal, rose 2.8 percent to 2,775 rupiah
and PT Adaro Energy (ADRO IJ), Indonesia’s second-biggest coal
producer, increased 3.2 percent to 2,450 rupiah.  Crude oil for April delivery rose for a fifth day, adding
as much as 0.9 percent to $96.25 a barrel in after-hours trading
in  New York . A higher oil price improves the appeal of
alternative fuels such as coal.  PT AKR Corporindo (AKRA IJ), an Indonesian chemical
distributor, jumped 8.1 percent to 1,600 rupiah, the biggest
increase since Nov. 6, 2009. AKR will pay a special interim
dividend of 135 rupiah a share on March 29 to shareholders on
record as of March 16, it said in a statement to the exchange.  PT Bank Central Asia (BBCA IJ),  Indonesia ’s largest bank by
market value, climbed 2.4 percent to 6,400 rupiah. Its unit PT
BCA Finance hired DBS Group Holdings Ltd., Standard Chartered
Plc and Trans Asia to help it sell 1.5 trillion rupiah ($169
million) of bonds, according to a person familiar with the
matter. BCA Finance President Director Roni Haslim confirmed the
plan after the market closed.  PT Indofood CBP Sukses Makmur (ICBP IJ), the nation’s
largest instant-noodle maker, rose 2.3 percent to 4,525 rupiah.
Wheat for May delivery plunged by the most allowed on the
Chicago Board of Trade yesterday, dropping as much as 7 percent
to $7.9575 a bushel. Indofood uses wheat to make instant
noodles.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Berni Moestafa in Jakarta at 
